\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The shuttle emerges from its narrow shaft into a busy residential area. The residential zone is in a massive tunnel several hundred yards across, and packed with tents and corrugated metal shacks. The light is artificially generated, cast from large square panels hung on the ceiling of the cave. }
