\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Even if they could buy a red robe, the color is just to remind people of their place. To actually take advantage of a privilege, you'd be scanned. Impersonating a higher caste is a crime, man.}
